      out.write("                    <h4><a href=\"https://wso2.com/api-management/\"><strong>About WSO2 API Manager</strong></a></h4>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>WSO2 API Manager (referred hereafter as &ldquo;API-M &rdquo;) is an open source enterprise-class solution that supports API publishing, lifecycle management, application development, access control, rate limiting, and analytics in one cleanly integrated system.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom-double\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h2 id=\"privacy-policy\"><strong>Privacy Policy</strong></h2>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>This section explains how API-M captures your personal information, purpose of capturing, and the retention of your personal information.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>Please note that this policy is for reference only, and is applicable for the software as a product. WSO2 Inc., or its developers have no access to the information held within API-M. Please refer &ldquo;Disclaimer&rdquo; for more information.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>Entities, organisations or individuals controlling the use and administration of API-M should create their own privacy policies setting out the manner in which data is controlled or processed by the respective entity, organisation or individual.</p>                    \n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom-double\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h2 id=\"what-are-the-personal-information\">What are the personal information &quest;</h2>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>API-M considers anything related to you as your personal information. This includes, but is not limited to,</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <ul>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>Your user name (except in the case where your user name is created by your employer under contract)</li>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>The IP address you use to login</li>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>Your device ID, if you choose to login with a device (Phone, Tablet)</li>\n");
      out.write("                    </ul>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>However API-M does not consider the following as your personal information, and  uses this only for <strong>analytical purposes</strong>, since this information cannot be used to track you.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <ul>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>City/Country from which your TCP/IP connection originates</li>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>Time of the day you login.(Year, Month, Week, Hour or Minute)</li>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>Type of the device you use to login (Phone, Tablet, etc.)</li>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>Operating system and Generic browser information</li>\n");
      out.write("                    </ul>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom-double\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h2 id=\"collection-of-your-information\">Collection of your information</h2>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>API-M collects your information to only serve your access requirements.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>For example,</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <ul>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>API-M uses your IP address to detect any suspicious login attempt to your account. </li>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>API-M uses your First Name, Last Name, etc to provide rich and personalized information.</li>\n");
      out.write("                    </ul>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h3 id=\"tracking-technologies\">Tracking Technologies</h3>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>API-M collects your information through the following,</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <ul>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>The user sign up page where you enter your personal data</li>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>Tracking your IP address with HTTP request, HTTP headers, and TCP/IP</li>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>Tracking your geographic information with the IP address</li>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>Your login history with browser cookies. Please refer our <strong>cookie policy</strong> for more information</li>\n");
      out.write("                    </ul>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom-double\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h2 id=\"user-of-your-personal-information\">Use of your personal information</h2>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>API-M will use your personal information only for the purposes for which it was collected (or for a use identified as consistent with that purpose).</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>API-M uses your personal information only for the following purposes.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <ul>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>To provide you with a personalized user experience. API-M uses attributes such as your name for this purpose</li>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>To protect your account from unauthorized access or a potential hacking attempt. API-M use HTTP or TCP/IP Headers  for this purpose</li>\n");
      out.write("                        <ul>\n");
      out.write("                            <li>This includes,</li>\n");
      out.write("                            <ul>\n");
      out.write("                                <li>IP address,</li>\n");
      out.write("                                <li>Browser fingerprinting,</li>\n");
      out.write("                                <li>Cookies</li>\n");
      out.write("                            </ul>\n");
      out.write("                        </ul>\n");
      out.write("                        <li>To derive statistical data for analytical purposes on system performance improvements. API-M will not keep any personal information after statistical calculations. Thus a statistical report has no means to identify an individual person</li>\n");
      out.write("                        <ul>\n");
      out.write("                            <li>API-M may use</li>\n");
      out.write("                            <ul>\n");
      out.write("                                <li>The IP Address to derive geographic information</li>\n");
      out.write("                                <li>Browser fingerprinting to determine the browser technology and version</li>\n");
      out.write("                            </ul>\n");
      out.write("                        </ul>\n");
      out.write("                    </ul>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom-double\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h2 id=\"disclosure-of-your-personal-information\">Disclosure of your personal information</h2>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>API-M will disclose personal information only for the purposes for which it was collected (or for a use identified as consistent with that purpose), unless you have consented otherwise or where it is required by law.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h3 id=\"legal-process\">Legal process</h3>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>API-M  may disclose your personal information with or without your consent where it is required by law following the due and lawful process.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom-double\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h2 id=\"how-apim-store-or-keep-your-personal-information\">How API-M keeps your personal information</h2>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h3 id=\"where-your-personal-information-stored\">Where your personal information is stored</h3>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>API-M stores your personal information in secured databases. API-M exercises proper industry accepted security measures to protect the database where your personal information is held.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>API-M may use encryption to keep your personal data with added level of security.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h3 id=\"how-long-does-apim-keep-your-personal-information\">How long does API-M keep your personal information &quest;</h3>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>API-M keep your personal data as long as you are an active user of our system. You can update your personal data at any time with the given self-care user portals.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h3 id=\"how-can-you-request-a-removal-of-your-personal-information\">How can you request a removal of your personal information &quest;</h3>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>You can request the administrator to delete your account The administrator will be the administrator of the tenant you are registered or the super-administrator if you do not use the tenant feature.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <p>You can additionally request to anonymize all traces of your activities that may have been retained by API-M  in Logs, Databases or Analytical storage.</p>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom-double\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h2 id=\"about\">About</h2>\n");
      out.write("                    <div class=\"margin-bottom\"></div>\n");
      out.write("                    <h3 id=\"changes-to-this-policy\">Changes to this policy</h3>\n");
